data.description: Beautiful 4 bed/2 bath home located on 4 acres of flat topography, with its stunning mountain views and 7 years of prepaid  solar.  Home has an open floorplan- perfect for entertaining. Kitchen has tons of cabinets for storage, island with breakfast bar, gas stove, and more! update lighting, ceiling fans and lots of natural night throughout the home.   Beautiful ceramic tile in the main living areas. Split bedroom floorplan.   Primary bath has a walk-in closet, while the hall features a tub/shower combo.  2 car attached garage w/ washer and dryer attachments. Lots of space in the backyard to build your dream backyard.   Get ready to pack your bags and don't forget your four-legged friends!
